999
01:29:42,482 --> 01:29:44,482
「さよなら」なんて
Something like 'goodbye'

1000
01:29:44,782 --> 01:29:49,082
まだ言えないまま 魔法が解けていく
Without being able to say it yet, the magic is fading away

1001
01:29:49,082 --> 01:29:53,282
バラバラになって 花になって 風に溶けていく
Falling apart, becoming flowers, dissolving into the wind

1002
01:29:53,782 --> 01:29:57,782
手を振れないまま 黙って立っている
Standing silently without being able to wave

1003
01:29:58,082 --> 01:30:00,282
私を連れて
Take me along

1004
01:30:00,330 --> 01:30:01,230
私を忘れて
Forget me

1005
01:30:01,230 --> 01:30:02,430
連れて すぐに
Take me away, quickly

1006
01:30:16,930 --> 01:30:20,330
伝えたい想いを声に出したって
Even if I were to voice the feelings I want to convey,

1007
01:30:20,330 --> 01:30:22,730
こんな言葉なんて言えないんだろう
I probably couldn't say such words.

1008
01:30:23,430 --> 01:30:26,830
大事に思ってしまうからずっと
Because I treasure them so much, I've always

1009
01:30:26,830 --> 01:30:30,130
大事なことが伝わらないんじゃないかって
worried that the most important things wouldn't get across.

1010
01:30:32,130 --> 01:30:33,530
知らない
I don't know,

1011
01:30:34,130 --> 01:30:35,630
知らない
I don't know.

1012
01:30:36,330 --> 01:30:41,530
知りたくもないことばっかで 胸が裂けていく
With so many things I don't even want to know, my heart is tearing apart.

1013
01:30:42,130 --> 01:30:48,130
ズタズタになって 痛いくらいに 愛しくなっていく
Being torn to shreds, it starts to hurt as I love you even more.

1014
01:30:48,630 --> 01:30:53,130
手も触れないまま 不確かにしてしまう
Leaving it uncertain, without even being able to touch your hand.

1015
01:30:53,430 --> 01:30:54,330
ごめんね ごめんね
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

1016
01:30:55,130 --> 01:30:57,730
いつか 時間が経ってみたら
If some time passes,

1017
01:30:57,730 --> 01:31:00,130
なんでもないって顔をして
I'll put on a face as if it's nothing.

1018
01:31:00,330 --> 01:31:04,830
寂しさも 痛みすらも 抜け落ちて過去になる
Both the loneliness and even the pain will fall away and become the past.

1019
01:31:05,430 --> 01:31:10,330
いつしかそんな日が来たら そんな時が来るなら
If such a day comes eventually, if such a time comes,

1020
01:31:10,330 --> 01:31:13,330
だったら今は
then for now...

1021
01:31:14,830 --> 01:31:18,730
どうしようもないくらいに 君を想っている
I'm thinking of you so much that I can't help it.

1022
01:31:19,130 --> 01:31:23,530
思い出になんて ならないくらい 君で出来ている
So much that it won't even become a memory, I'm made of you.

1023
01:31:24,130 --> 01:31:28,330
ずっと気づいてた 気づいてしまったんだ
I've always known, I've finally realized it.

1024
01:31:28,730 --> 01:31:30,830
「忘れて」なんてね
To say "forget me"...

1025
01:31:31,130 --> 01:31:32,330
嘘だ
...was a lie.

1026
01:31:32,730 --> 01:31:36,530
愛しさが 胸を焦がしていく
This love is burning my heart.

1027
01:31:36,830 --> 01:31:41,130
傷になったって 覚えていて 忘れないでいて
Even if it becomes a scar, please remember, please don't forget.

1028
01:31:41,330 --> 01:31:45,630
もう言えないから 今、愛を伝う
Because I can't say it anymore, I'll convey my love now.

1029
01:31:46,130 --> 01:31:48,530
笑って また会おう
Let's meet again with a smile.

1030
01:31:48,830 --> 01:31:51,130
さようなら
Goodbye.

1031
01:31:51,530 --> 01:31:54,830
さようなら
Goodbye.

1032
01:31:56,130 --> 01:31:58,830
みんな本当に、本当に、めっちゃ大好きだ。
Everyone, really, really, I love you so much.

1033
01:31:59,530 --> 01:32:03,830
最後まで見てくれて本当にありがとうございました。
Thank you so much for watching until the very end.

1034
01:32:04,330 --> 01:32:07,830
この6年半、約7年、応援してくれてありがとう。
Thank you for supporting me for these six and a half years, nearly seven years.

1035
01:32:08,130 --> 01:32:10,530
ずっと見てくれてありがとう。
Thank you for always watching.

1036
01:32:10,830 --> 01:32:13,530
ずっと愛してくれてありがとう。
Thank you for always loving me.

1037
01:32:13,830 --> 01:32:16,830
バイバイ！またね！
Bye-bye! See you again!

